gurU-sMq dI ikrpw nwl sB qoN au~cI Awqmk AvsQw iml jWdI hY ]2]
prmwqmw ny Awp ijs mnu`K dI shwieqw kIqI,
aus ny prmwqmw dy BgqW dI crnIN l`g ky Awqmk AwnMd mwixAw[
auhnW dy AMdroN (jdoN) Awpw-Bwv dUr ho igAw qdoN auh prmwqmw dw rUp hI ho gey,
jyhVy mnu`K dieAw dy ^zwny prmwqmw dI srn Aw pey ]3]
jdoN iksy mnu`K nUM (gurU dI ikrpw nwl) auh prmwqmw hI iml pYNdw hY ijs nUM auh imlxw cwhuMdw hY,
qdoN auh (bwhr jMglW phwVW Awidk ivc aus nUM) l`Bx leI nhIN jWdw[
(prmwqmw nUM Awpxy AMdr hI l`B lYx vwly mnu`K) Afol-ic`q ho jWdy hn, auh sdw AwnMd AvsQw ivc itky rihMdy hn,
hy nwnk! gurU dI ikrpw nwl auh sdw suKW ivc v`sx vwly ho jWdy hn ]4]110]
