aus ny (mwno) kRoVW qIrQW ivc cu`BIAW lw leIAW, kRoVW qIrQW dy ieSnwn kr ley,
aus ny (mwno) l`KW rupey ArbW rupey KrbW rupey dwn kr ley,
ijs mnu`K dy mn ivc prmwqmw dw nwm Aw v`sdw hY ]1]
isRStI dy pwlxhwr pRBU dy gux gw ky swry mnu`K pivqR ho skdy hn[
dieAw dy somy gurU dI srn ipAW (swry) pwp imt jWdy hn ] rhwau]
aus ny (mwno) pu`Ty ltk ky AnykW qpW dy swDn swD ley,
aus ny (mwno, ir`DIAW is`DIAW dy) AnykW lwB K`t ley, AnykW mnorQ hwsl kr ley,
jyhVw mnu`K AwpxI jIB nwl prmwqmw dw nwm jpdw hY ]2]
aus ny (mwno) isimRqIAW SwsqRW vydW dy aucwrn kr ley,
aus ny (mwno) jog (dIAW guMJlW) dI sUJ pRwpq kr leI, aus ny (mwno) is`DW nUM imly suKW nwl sWJ pw leI,
ijs mnu`K dw mn prmwqmw dw nwm ismridAW ismridAW prmwqmw nwl ig`J jWdw hY ]3]
(ijs mnu`K auqy pRBU ikrpw krdw hY, auh mnu`K) aus AQwh hsqI vwly AphuMc qy byAMq prmwqmw dw nwm jpdw hY,
aus dw nwm Awpxy ihrdy ivc itkWdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik myry auqy ikrpw kr (qW ik mYN qyrw nwm jp skW) ]4]111]
