(goibMd dw AwrwDn gurU dI rwhIN hI imldw hY[) aus ny goibMd dw nwm ismr ismr ky Awqmk AwnMd mwixAw hY,
(ijs mnu`K ny) gurU dy sohxy crn Awpxy ihrdy ivc vswey hn ]1]
goibMd pwrbRhmu (sB hsqIAW nwloN) v`fw hY, swry guxW dw mwlk hY (aus ivc koeI iksy iksm dI Gwt nhIN hY)[
aus goibMd nUM AwrwD ky myrw mn hOsly vwlw bx jWdw hY (qy AnykW iklibKW dw twkrw krn jogw ho jWdw hY) ] rhwau]
mYN qW hr vyly gurU dw nwm cyqy r`Kdw hW (gurU dI imhr nwl hI goibMd dw ismrn pRwpq huMdw hY, qy)
aus ismrn dI brkiq nwl swry kMmW ivc sPlqw hwsl huMdI hY ]2]
(gurU dI rwhIN hr QW prmwqmw dw) drsn kr ky (drsn krn vwly) TMFy Twr mn vwly ho jWdy hn,
qy auhnW dy AnykW (pihly) jnmW dy kIqy hoey pwp nws ho jWdy hn ]3]
hy nwnk! (gurU dI srn pY ky goibMd dw nwm ismirAW dunIAw vwly) swry fr-^qry mn qoN lih jWdy hn,
(ikauNik) ismrn dI brkiq nwl ieh XkIn bx jWdw hY ik (goibMd Awpxy syvk dI Awp lwj r`Kdw hY ]4]112]
